Hi guys, I have trained my cnn model with tf.estimator and tf.data API. Model's input is an one-shot iterator. The relative model files(ckpt, meta, index) have been saved in model_dir. Now I want to predict one or more images' label using the trained model.

Any instructions for this?

Hi guys, I have trained my cnn model with `tf.estimator` and `tf.data` API. Model's input is an one-shot iterator. The relative model files(ckpt, meta, index) have been saved in `model_dir`. **Now I want to predict one or more images' label using the trained model.**

Any instructions for this?
